data.description: Welcome to Florida Pines. This quiet community sits right off of US 27 and less than 20 minutes to the world’s most famous theme park, Disney World. As you step into this four bedroom, two bath open floor plan, you will fall in love with a beautiful engineered hardwood floors that flow throughout the living areas and the porcelain tiles in the kitchen. One of my favorite features about this home are the tall cathedral ceilings that flow throughout the home. You will also love lounging by your heated pool and watching those Florida sunsets as you relax on your covered lanai. Wanting a second property as possibly a short term rental? Well, you’re in luck because this property has the ability for short term rental. With being close to attractions like Legoland, Margaritaville, Disney World, and all the other great developments happening on US 27. This home also has the ability to offer an assumable loan.  With a new roof from 2023, a newer Ac and water heater. This home is ready for it’s new buyer.
